data.description: MLS# 271649 What an amazing find located on a corner lot in West Pasco! Single level home with oversized 3 car garage and 50X30 shop all on over 1/2 flat acres! This charming home has stucco siding, and an adorable wrap around covered  porch to enjoy the morning sun and beautiful evening sunsets. Walking in you will be wowed by the wide foyer and hallways with white painted wainscoting. Engineered hardwood floor flows from foyer to dining and hallways. Interior has been freshly painted. The kitchen is spacious with beautiful white cabinets including convenient pull outs. Under cabinet lighting displays the newer subway tile backsplash. Corner sink with upgraded faucet. Unique lighting and decorative barn wood features. Newer stainless double oven range and refrigerator. So much space to entertain. And don't forget that pantry for storage. Lovely formal dining room that opens to the living room area. Cozy gas fireplace with newer insert to stay warm on those chilly days. French doors leads to the spacious patio with newer privacy wall. Moving down the extra wide hallway you will find 4 spacious rooms. Main bathroom includes vanity and tub/surround. Dual master suites or mother in law space. Master bedroom is oversized with dual closets. Master bath features vanity and walk in shower. Additional suite includes its own bathroom with single sink and tub/surround. Laundry room is spacious and includes counter space and utility sink. Laundry leads to the 3 car garage. And don't miss that 1/2 bath located inside the garage. Exterior includes so much parking/RV space. RV plug in and dump site. Backyard is newly fenced with underground timed sprinklers. AND THAT GARDEN! Grow your own vegetables! Drip lines are already installed. Shop is huge! Store whatever your heart desires! Additional storage 8X14 deep storage shed included for all your yard tools and mowers. Other features include ,HVAC newer compressor, humidifier and air scrubber installed. Home is complete with central vacuum as well. This home has so much to offer. Don't miss seeing this gem!
